Name: Average resolution time following 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Accepted + In Progress' activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average delay time caused by 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the entire incident resolution process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of incidents involving 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Closed' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum resolution time of incidents starting with 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Cycle time of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the context of the VINST system
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time in 'Unmatched + Unmatched' for incidents exceeding average resolution time
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
